    public interface RequestManager
    Interface that imposes operations of requesting and returning elements.
    Author:
    (original) Daniel Gomes, Filipe Maia, Pedro Antunes, (revisionSOLID) Eva Gomes, Hugo Leal, Lucas Andrade

    • Method Summary

      Requests an element from this.

      • requestElement

        Element requestElement(Element element)
        Requests an element from this.
        Parameters:
        element - The element to be requested.
        Returns:
        element if the requiring operation was successful;
        null if it couldn't be requested.

      • returnElement

        boolean returnElement(Element element)
        Returns an element to this, if it was previously requested.
        Parameters:
        element - The element to be returned.
        Returns:
        true if the returning operation was successful;
        false if it couldn't be returned.
